1. *Mrze* ga svi u ovoj školi. (Everyone in this school hates him.)
2. Oni *mrze* da čekaju na red. (They hate waiting in line.)
3. Njemu *mrze* kad ga neko kritikuje. (He hates being criticized by anyone.)
4. Ja *mrzim* kad se raspravljate oko gluposti. (I hate when you argue over silly things.)
5. Mi *mrzimo* kad ljudi ne poštuju dogovor. (We hate it when people don't respect the agreement.)
6. Ti *mrziš* da kasniš na sastanak. (You hate being late for a meeting.)
7. Oni *mrzeli* taj grad jer su imali loša iskustva tamo. (They used to hate that city because they had bad experiences there.)
8. Njima *mrzeće* se život kad vide koliko su novca potrošili. (They will hate their life when they see how much money they spent.)
9. *Mrzim* kada me neko laže. (I hate it when someone lies to me.)
10. Nije da *mrzim* sport, ali jednostavno nisam zainteresovan. (It's not that I hate sports, but I'm just not interested.)